      "title": "Recipe -> Widgets -> Generate",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Load recipe and generate\n\n1. Fill token + asset_id in `Load Asset From GenAsset`.\n2. Queue once. `Load Recipe To Widgets` will output prompt, negative, sampler values, and width/height.\n3. Those outputs are already linked into CLIP/KSampler/EmptyLatent widget inputs.\n4. Queue again to generate with loaded recipe values.\n5. Optional: `Save To GenAsset` saves the new result as a new version.\n\nNotes:\n- `model_name` is extracted but checkpoint selection stays manual in `Load Checkpoint` for maximum compatibility.\n- If your ComfyUI warns about deprecated widget input APIs, update extension/plugins and restart ComfyUI."
      ],
      "color": "#243",
      "bgcolor": "#355"
    }
